{"tid":33424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何追求不同星座女孩","createTime":"2016-12-10T19:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T09:44:43.000Z","uid":21255,"like":41,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"986c9ceabaa56be9bcacd52e548e429aa26d336e","tid":33424,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"上集同大家探討完星座日常建議 今次講下點追女仔<br />\n<br />\n水瓶座<br />\n水瓶座本身就滿滿的份 不需要喝太多水 也不要叫水瓶座喝水 喝水太多的水瓶座最終都會死<br />\n<br />\n雙魚座<br />\n浪漫主義的雙魚座女孩很愛幻想 亦很愛想像 想要追求雙魚座女孩 請將自己化身一位有錢有樣的王子<br />\n<br />\n白羊座<br />\n白羊座的女孩總是博愛而溫柔的 她們從不介意替你分擔錢太多的煩惱 大方的向心儀女孩展示你的存摺吧<br />\n<br />\n金牛座<br />\n固執的金牛座女孩會有點脾氣 多些分享港女語錄吧 固執的她們會覺得你很了解她們<br />\n<br />\n雙子座<br />\n雙子座的女孩精神很脆弱 很神經質 但存摺往往能令她們安心 多利用存摺吧 （數字太少會有反效果）<br />\n<br />\n巨蟹座<br />\n巨蟹座的女孩很容易自卑 你要多些鼓勵她 最好的鼓勵方法時每星期都帶巨蟹座女孩到半島自助餐的長腳蟹吧<br />\n<br />\n獅子座<br />\n想追獅子座女孩 可以跟著我叫：Roooooar roar roar， 還有記得把頭髮染金並電爆炸頭"},{"pid":"7653e8fc6460eed0a38a96f99f22571a7c52d855","tid":33424,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182396d005a03759fb53e3a5b57e85c014d0cc5","tid":33424,"uid":37029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:18:20.000Z","msg":"高汁抽水 留名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔睇真啲都俾你呃到負皮"},{"pid":"030838bf5f7f4ae3212b67b866cfc3c434c68d84","tid":33424,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:21:02.000Z","msg":"幹禁錯制post左<br />\n<br />\n處女座<br />\n處女座的女孩都是完美主義者 不是處女的她們也會將自己幻想成處女一樣矜貴 因為她們追求完美 也追求你存摺的完美<br />\n<br />\n天秤座<br />\n善辯的天秤座女孩很常見 辯贏她們的最佳方法 便是拿著一疊金牛拍打她們那小賤嘴<br />\n<br />\n天蠍座<br />\n口是心非的天蠍座女孩 想讓她們誠實的唯一方法 就是你自己先要對她們誠實 誠實的展示自己的存摺吧<br />\n<br />\n獵戶座<br />\n獵戶座的女孩很容易情緒失控 不要追求 除非你有令她們安定的樣子<br />\n<br />\n摩羯座<br />\n摩羯座的女孩都很愛獨立 要進佔她們的人生不容易 可以試試買兩張馬爾代夫的卡塔爾航空頭等機票 請她去度個假吧<br />\n<br />\n蛇夫座<br />\n蛇夫座的女孩充滿罪疚感 因為她們的出現令不少人改變了出生以來數十年的個性 嘗試令她們別看得自己那麼高<br />\n<br />\n關愛座<br />\n富愛心的關愛座女孩 只要到65歲自然手到拿來"},{"pid":"7da00162e35f6a836b4e5af2199b0ae554109db7","tid":33424,"uid":7744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:45:17.000Z","msg":"蛇夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829824d2f3587a3fb472fecfe34ec581cc664b67","tid":33424,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:07:28.000Z","msg":"關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d58cc8a9a1c23143f2f480174a72e1a48640ea9","tid":33424,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:09:21.000Z","msg":"超準的XD"},{"pid":"e82db515a90a4b059828d757d8825acd5df31d42","tid":33424,"uid":29191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f83c7b679652b109a9e3921c7f52c679f6f7d6","tid":33424,"uid":11435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:14:16.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427cf68aa43516bf45159d